    "The National Institute of Education Sciences, linked to the Ministry of Education, founded the STEM Education Research Center the following year.",
    "This center plays a crucial role in advising on policy and driving the theoretical and practical advancements needed to establish China as a leader in STEM education.",
    "However, the extent of its impact remains underexplored in the literature (Ministry of Education [MOE], P. R. of China, 2016).",
    "The Information Technology Education Professional Committee of the China Association for Educational Technology established the \"Special Interest Group of Makers and Interdisciplinary Education\" (SIG-MIE) in 2022.",
    "This group combines hands-on, experiential learning with traditional STEM subjects to foster students' innovation and critical thinking skills."
  ],
